 The Touch of Gold Jewellery Store in Middelburg Mall was robbed on the 18th of October. Three men charged in and smashed the display cases with hammers and stole an undisclosed amount of goods. Also read: VIDEO: Eyewitness shares robbery video Mall customers were alarmed by what sounded like gunshots and smoke.
